                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "托萝莎是逐影庭的雇员。曾担任巡轨船导览员，后来成为了一名证物管理员。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4723,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "«Дуга»",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "智能测谎机。托萝莎想带他多观察人类如何说谎，并帮助他突破莫索协议，成为真正的\"人类\"。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "让克",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "《蒸汽鸟报》的编辑。投诉过托萝莎讲起话\"像乌鸦一样难听\"。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
